skdetail:

Invocation Name: motivate me
des:
What are you going to do today? Get motivated, get inspired and do something great! 

Motivate Me is here to give Alexa the ability to empower your day with carefully curated quotes credited with their authors. 

Whatever it is you want to do, you can do it ⭐
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
